OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeople can't wait for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fenergy help - Citizens     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FAdvice                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Many households cannot wait for the    
OL,6, government to decide whether more      
OL,7, support will be given to cope with     
OL,8, energy bills, Citizens Advice has said.
OL,10,FThe charity said it made more food bank
OL,11,Freferrals and crisis support in July   
OL,12,Fthan it had in 2019 and 2020 combined. 
OL,14,FThe warning comes after the industry   
OL,15,Fregulator said energy bills could start
OL,16,Fto rise at the end of this month, more 
OL,17,Fthan five weeks earlier than thought.  
OL,19,FA government meeting on Thursday with  
OL,20,Fenergy firms yielded no firm action.   
